Women4Cyber is hosting its next conference in Athens in collaboration with Women4Cyber Greece! Join us for cutting-edge discussions on cybersecurity, AI, cybercrime, and more. Connect through inspiring talks, real-world case studies, and networking opportunities. A VIP C-level networking space will also be available.

Join us for the 3rd edition of the Women4Cyber Annual Conference — a unique European forum connecting cybersecurity professionals, industry leaders, and policymakers.
 
This year, we’re meeting in Athens for two days of expert panels, practical sessions, and valuable networking opportunities focused on the key challenges and developments in cybersecurity.
 
⚠️ Please note: This is an in-person event only. Remote attendance will not be available.
 
What to Expect:
Expert-led sessions on AI, cybercrime, resilience, and more
C-level networking and partner side events
Access to the full conference programme and exhibition area
